||\cdot||
||x|| := \langle x, x \rangle
||x+y||^2 = \langle x + y, x + y \rangle = \langle x, x \rangle + \langle x, y \rangle + \langle y, x \rangle + \langle y, y \rangle
||x-y||^2 =  \langle x - y, x - y \rangle = \langle x, x \rangle - \langle x, y \rangle - \langle y, x \rangle + \langle y, y \rangle
||x+y||^2 + ||x-y||^2 = 2||x||^2 + 2||y||^2.
L^p
p \neq 2
\langle \cdot,\cdot\rangle
V
\Vert x\Vert^{2}=\langle x,x\rangle
